{"tid":356003,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［ 新手有圖 ] 養睫角守宮bb問題 ！","createTime":"2017-08-11T17:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T17:25:56.000Z","uid":130924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0797385f1b9c040ab32ece8737efe507e11d74b","tid":356003,"uid":130924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T17:20:39.000Z","msg":"幾個星期前先上網買咗隻睫角手宮bb。<br />\n佢好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，乜都食<br />\n但係最弊係佢好鐘意亂跳，走得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  成功上到手，但又會咬我，有時又唔小心夾到佢，佢慘叫咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/010722_03588df8aee4f772fb3a186bd80c106c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F010722_03588df8aee4f772fb3a186bd80c106c.jpg&h=8a2980fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想請教養開嘅巴絲打，係咪幼體通常都唔定性，好鐘意亂跳亂走，上手又有啲咩技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 養到成體通常幾奈？"},{"pid":"9d5424df9a02bc1a5cf8710218f457f2d446bf33","tid":356003,"uid":130924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T17:26:18.000Z","msg":"呢隻係我嘅睫角bb<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/012458_6d1ead39a94266e04b2c9ad8a1fc36a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F012458_6d1ead39a94266e04b2c9ad8a1fc36a9.jpg&h=11226b09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/012538_db5c438d1357cd04313881140c848f39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F012538_db5c438d1357cd04313881140c848f39.jpg&h=fdb08df6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/012612_3da7c64b6964213cca2e18efae3ad910.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2